{"tid":2364412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向華強：「我年紀大了，應該找些不顯眼而且低調又年輕的人做特工」","createTime":"2021-01-13T03:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T20:56:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":303,"uniUserReply":146,"replies":[{"pid":"82ad2e1108b9ffb7f101d82453e6a87fe897029c","tid":2364412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"台灣女星郭碧婷2019年嫁給香港娛樂大亨向華強長子向佐，去年10月生下寶貝女兒「小奶皇」，本月9日在台北舉行郭碧婷的歸寧宴以及孩子的百日宴，向華強和向佐申請依親居留，卻因政治立場親中，被疑中共任務性移民，對此向華強回應了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qFcvt1UJFI3TtWxQGLy3Pg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxMC4zMTI1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Vm2UrwLIwnCtFJFOlG5AlQ--~B/aD02NTE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/chinatimes.com.tw/2faafaf6c68d9f06956668133f334f4f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqFcvt1UJFI3TtWxQGLy3Pg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxMC4zMTI1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVm2UrwLIwnCtFJFOlG5AlQ--~B%2FaD02NTE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fchinatimes.com.tw%2F2faafaf6c68d9f06956668133f334f4f&h=d623b5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n向太陳嵐10日於微博發文，誇獎台灣疫情控制得最好，讓他們能舉辦兩百多人的喜宴，並替老公和兒子辦依親居留證，「要不然兩個男的回香港就來不了台北了。」想不到有意人士揣測中共任務性移民，向太特別為老公闢謠，「向華強說：『我年紀大了，73歲已退休，還有一點錢，為什麼要做特工呢？應該找些不顯眼而且低調又年輕的人做特工吧？』」向太相信台灣政府英明，不會拿媒體報導來做為證據依歸，表明一家人依親居留是合情合理的權益，「不是（能）因為疫情發生，大家都在鎖國、鎖簽證的情況下，總是想個辦法解決親人的團聚啊！尤其這個爺爺是這麼愛小奶皇的情況下！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，那麼多人申請過台灣依親居留，為什麼向華強父子就被指特工呢？原來向華強的父親向前年輕時參加過抗日戰爭，曾是軍統特務，抗戰勝利後，又到香港從事間諜活動，因此向華強父子爆出有統戰背景，連專業移民代辦公司都坦言身份特殊的話，可能就不會批准申請。<br />\n<br />\n對此陸委會發言人邱垂正表示主管機關還在了解中，尚未做出最後的決定；向華強父子能否申請到依親居請，引起外界持續關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rYKj3EByaFMl6JVWioQNSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOS4zNzU-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/.Uybv.xfuoICIErbi.TbfQ--~B/aD02NTA7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/chinatimes.com.tw/6922a2756bc4876d6045004e1bf2b9e9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrYKj3EByaFMl6JVWioQNSA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOS4zNzU-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.Uybv.xfuoICIErbi.TbfQ--~B%2FaD02NTA7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fchinatimes.com.tw%2F6922a2756bc4876d6045004e1bf2b9e9&h=7f9ce1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向華強、向佐依親來台參加郭碧婷的歸寧宴、孩子的百日宴。(翻攝自向太陳嵐微博)<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/向華強被爆有統戰背景-申請來台長期居留遭抺紅無奈回應-015104104.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%90%91%E8%8F%AF%E5%BC%B7%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E6%9C%89%E7%B5%B1%E6%88%B0%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%B0%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B1%85%E7%95%99%E9%81%AD%E6%8A%BA%E7%B4%85%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-015104104.html&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=de4eafe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/向華強被爆有統戰背景-申請來台長期居留遭抺紅無奈回應-015104104.html</a>"},{"pid":"dac072ec5e25f5cf01cae881d5cf3dab3e16ff16","tid":2364412,"uid":17359,"like":176,"dislike":1,"score":175,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:33:14.000Z","msg":"肉撚酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90afd5417e1d55e1df5d3832cf8a31be4f164e71","tid":2364412,"uid":61032,"like":217,"dislike":2,"score":215,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"咁愛國好心就死去大灣區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3dd534c139a2c145cd96d8d23d25e0d7905edb","tid":2364412,"uid":49329,"like":151,"dislike":2,"score":149,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"咁愛國，唔解唔死返支那?"},{"pid":"f9a1ef1629f367520edb7cfff6f0db00ccb41fa6","tid":2364412,"uid":253016,"like":146,"dislike":2,"score":144,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:45:30.000Z","msg":"應該找些不顯眼而且低調又年輕的人做特工吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賤畜仲要反咬班後生一口"},{"pid":"f16316dea6abe7ae81d9712f772947d5d3af5413","tid":2364412,"uid":512