%2FVm2UrwLIwnCtFJFOlG5AlQ--~B%2FaD02NTE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fchinatimes.com.tw%2F2faafaf6c68d9f06956668133f334f4f&h=d623b5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n向太陳嵐10日於微博發文，誇獎台灣疫情控制得最好，讓他們能舉辦兩百多人的喜宴，並替老公和兒子辦依親居留證，「要不然兩個男的回香港就來不了台北了。」想不到有意人士揣測中共任務性移民，向太特別為老公闢謠，「向華強說：『我年紀大了，73歲已退休，還有一點錢，為什麼要做特工呢？應該找些不顯眼而且低調又年輕的人做特工吧？』」向太相信台灣政府英明，不會拿媒體報導來做為證據依歸，表明一家人依親居留是合情合理的權益，「不是（能）因為疫情發生，大家都在鎖國、鎖簽證的情況下，總是想個辦法解決親人的團聚啊！尤其這個爺爺是這麼愛小奶皇的情況下！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，那麼多人申請過台灣依親居留，為什麼向華強父子就被指特工呢？原來向華強的父親向前年輕時參加過抗日戰爭，曾是軍統特務，抗戰勝利後，又到香港從事間諜活動，因此向華強父子爆出有統戰背景，連專業移民代辦公司都坦言身份特殊的話，可能就不會批准申請。<br />\n<br />\n對此陸委會發言人邱垂正表示主管機關還在了解中，尚未做出最後的決定；向華強父子能否申請到依親居請，引起外界持續關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rYKj3EByaFMl6JVWioQNSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOS4zNzU-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/.Uybv.xfuoICIErbi.TbfQ--~B/aD02NTA7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/chinatimes.com.tw/6922a2756bc4876d6045004e1bf2b9e9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrYKj3EByaFMl6JVWioQNSA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOS4zNzU-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.Uybv.xfuoICIErbi.TbfQ--~B%2FaD02NTA7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fchinatimes.com.tw%2F6922a2756bc4876d6045004e1bf2b9e9&h=7f9ce1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向華強、向佐依親來台參加郭碧婷的歸寧宴、孩子的百日宴。(翻攝自向太陳嵐微博)<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/向華強被爆有統戰背景-申請來台長期居留遭抺紅無奈回應-015104104.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%90%91%E8%8F%AF%E5%BC%B7%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E6%9C%89%E7%B5%B1%E6%88%B0%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%B0%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B1%85%E7%95%99%E9%81%AD%E6%8A%BA%E7%B4%85%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-015104104.html&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=de4eafe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/向華強被爆有統戰背景-申請來台長期居留遭抺紅無奈回應-015104104.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:19:20.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a73cc92f4e2b318135b838375db33eae690b9e9","tid":2364412,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"別讓向華強走了"},{"pid":"71a1cb785a5063e15f3864acca3016c01a4dccb3","tid":2364412,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"個condom用撚完就想走。<br />\n<br />\n中共屌香港屌都差唔多完，個condom走向撚咗，係唔係玩嘢。<br />\n<br />\n走唔到就全家諸九族"},{"pid":"5e680422d54122495c28624e0d692dfa59a1b156","tid":2364412,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"真係當自己龍五咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01638512081c6a1ea3aab6095e043fa438ae2018","tid":2364412,"uid":30762,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjeTUoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjeTUoO.jpg&h=ea17ee0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35f2d6281f8e4d4bf630932b067dda0499933570","tid":2364412,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"你講到自己咁愛國，但又走去你愛國嘅敵對地方<br />\n<br />\n你同我講如果你唔係特工，咁你愛緊嘅嗰個國家又點會放你走呢？<br />\n<br />\n而你又點解要背叛你愛緊嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e84e91ca0a826d62f1000359997f20f286d1ab","tid":2364412,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"愛國愛左去台灣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a947df512c5969457cc7a71d627d4a6c840683bf","tid":2364412,"uid":38609,"li